{"id":"SHENSHENGDEBEIXIJU5","scripts":[{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"この先はサディアの領域……","nameColor":"#a9f548","bgm":"battle-boss-italy","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"どうやらはぐれセイレーン艦隊はまだ出没しているようね…油断しないで挑むわ","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":5,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"flashin":{"1":5,"alpha":[1,0],"delay":0,"black":true,"dur":0.5},"dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":0.5},"say":"ロイヤルネイビーが、我がサディアのアズールレーンへの復帰を要請する、と？","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"そうよ。セイレーンに地中海が脅かされている今、手を取り合って共に闘うべきだわ","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"セイレーンに脅かされている？違うな。そうしてきたのはロイヤルではないか？","side":2,"expression":3,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"さっきも話したけど、我がロイヤルネイビーはあくまで航路の安全を第一に考えているわ。他意はないわよ","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":4,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"セイレーン襲来時に地中海に勢力を押し込みながら、膝元のアイリスと帝国の反目を座視したのはそちらロイヤルではなかったというのか？","side":2,"expression":3,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"そもそも、此度のセイレーンがこちらに進出したこと自体、ロイヤルがわざわざ「見落とした」とでも言い訳するつもり？","side":2,"expression":4,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"リットリオ、貴方は分かっているはずよ。量産型とはいえあの量のセイレーンがサディアに観測されるまで何の情報もないはずがないもの","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":7,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"side":2,"dir":1,"say":"沿岸部の索敵に観測されることなく、いきなり現れたということは…","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"地中海のどこかに鏡面海域が出現したのか？","side":2,"expression":5,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"ええ、我がロイヤルが地中海への入り口を両方押さえている以上、セイレーンの出現は鏡面海域からしかないわ","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"サディアの南部に最初に観測されたということは、東南部にそれが現れたという可能性が高いと思う","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"なるほど、ではロイヤルはどう動く？","side":2,"expression":4,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"…………これよりロイヤル艦隊がその捜索作戦を展開するわ","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"side":2,"dir":1,"say":"ならばサディア帝国海軍も参加させてもらおう","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"この地中海は我がサディア帝国の文明を育む海だ。セイレーンに汚されるわけにはいかない","side":2,"expression":7,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"この共同作戦を契機に、アズールレーン復帰への礎とする――この条件でどうだ？","side":2,"expression":8,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"…………","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":5,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"なに、ヴィシアの一件もあるからな。仲間の信頼を得るには時間が必要だよ","side":2,"expression":3,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"確かに貴方の言う通りね…サディアの加勢を認めるわ","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"地中海東南部に存在すると思われるセイレーンの前進拠点を捜索し、撃破する……","side":2,"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","actor":205029,"nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"というのが作戦の目的だけど、悪いけど一つ条件をつけさせてもらうわ","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":5,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"dir":1,"actorName":"ウォースパイト","say":"サディア帝国の戦艦による作戦の参加を禁止とするわ。違反する場合はロイヤルネイビーも相応の措置を取らせてもらう","nameColor":"#a9f548","side":2,"expression":4,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":205029,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"（ふん、一方的に自分ルールを押し付けてくるとは……ロイヤルらしいといえばロイヤルらしいね）","side":2,"expression":3,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"say":"（なに、今に見ていろ。このリットリオが貴方達全員を騙し通してみせる…！）","side":2,"expression":7,"dir":1,"actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgmDelay":2,"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"say":"リットリオ、首尾は大丈夫？私の助けが必要ですか？","nameColor":"#ffde38","bgm":"story-italy","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900198,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"ああ、計画通りに進んでいるよ","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"地中海の制海権を得るにはロイヤルの勢力を排除する必要がある。そのためにまずはマルタを手にする必要がある","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"あの島がロイヤルの手中にある限り、こちらの動きは逐一あのエリザベスに報告されることになるだろう","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":3,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"逆に言うと、マルタからロイヤルの勢力を排除できれば、もはや地中海はこのサディアの手にあるも同然だ","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"対セイレーン作戦には一部の兵力が参加し、ウォースパイトたちを安心させ、","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":8,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"同時に夜にタラント港に主力艦たちを移動させる","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"未明にはマルタを攻略し、ロイヤル艦隊が戻ってくるまでに作戦を完遂させればいい","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":8,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"いくらあの神速のウォースパイトでも即応できない","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"それもいいですけど、ロイヤルの艦隊と戦って勝てるのかしら…？","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":1,"expression":3,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900198,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"ヴェネト、総旗艦であるあなたがそこでためらっていてどうする？","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"サディア艦隊、そしてこのリットリオを信じればいいさ","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":3,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"なんなら今回の作戦だけ、私が総旗艦を代わりに務めてあげてもいいんだが？","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"あははは…またそんなことを言って……","actor":900198,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"おかげさまで決心が付きました。この「演目」、あなたの言う通りにしましょ？","actor":900198,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"あ、でも総旗艦は譲ってあげませんよ？","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":1,"expression":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900198,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"それはそうだな。貴方が決めていればそれでいい","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":6,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"ヴェネトが総旗艦を務めていれば、私も安心して戦いに集中できる。なに、軍議室で輝くか、戦場で輝くか、それだけの違いだ","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":1,"dir":1,"say":"ふふふ","actor":900198,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01},"bgName":"bg_story_italy","side":0,"dir":1,"say":"さあ、作戦が決まったら、最後に少し休憩でもしない？","actor":605020,"nameColor":"#ffde38"},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"少しお付き合いしていただいてもいいかな？――美しいシニョリーナよ","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":0,"expression":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":605020,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"bgName":"bg_story_italy","dir":1,"say":"ええ、喜んで～","nameColor":"#ffde38","side":1,"expression":4,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":900198,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}}],"fadein":1.5,"mode":2,"once":true}